msgid "Tuner"
msgstr "Tuner"

msgid "Internet Radio Player"
msgstr "Lecteur de Web Radios"

msgid "Listen to Radio Stations all over the world"
msgstr "Écoutez les stations de radio du monde entier"

msgid "Radio;Audio;Listen;Stations;Receiver;"
msgstr "Radio;Audio;Écouter;Stations;Récepteur;"

msgid "technosf"
msgstr ""

msgid "Internet Radio"
msgstr ""

msgid "Make finding and listening to internet radio stations fun again!"
msgstr ""
"Rendez la recherche et l’écoute des stations de radio Internet amusantes à "
"nouveau !"

msgid ""
"Instead of showing all the stations you already know, Tuner presents you a "
"new selection of stations from all over the world every time you hit the "
"Shuffle button."
msgstr ""
"Au lieu d’afficher toutes les stations que vous connaissez déjà, Tuner vous "
"présente une nouvelle sélection de stations du monde entier à chaque fois "
"que vous appuyez sur le bouton Shuffle."

msgid "Tuner uses the community-driven station catalog radio-browser.info."
msgstr ""
"Tuner utilise le catalogue communautaire de stations radio-browser.info."

msgid "Discover new stations every day"
msgstr "Découvrez de nouvelles stations chaque jour"

msgid "Star stations you like and visit their website"
msgstr ""
"Marquez les stations que vous aimez comme favorites et visitez leur site Web"

msgid "Control Tuner from your volume indicator"
msgstr "Contrôlez la lecture de Tuner depuis votre indicateur de volume"

msgid "Tuner with dark theme, discovery"
msgstr "Tuner avec thème sombre, découverte"

msgid "Tuner with light theme, starred stations"
msgstr "Tuner avec thème clair, stations favorites"

msgid "Tuner search for stations"
msgstr "Tuner recherchant des stations"

msgid "Tuner saved searches"
msgstr "Recherches enregistrées dans Tuner"

msgid "Tuner playing station metadata"
msgstr "Tuner affichant des métadonnées de la station"

msgid "Tuner preferences"
msgstr "Préférences dans Tuner"

msgid "Tuner station context information"
msgstr "Informations contextuelles d'une station Tuner"

msgid "Tuner jukebox station shuffle"
msgstr ""

msgid "Maintanance release:"
msgstr "Version de maintenance :"

msgid "Updated freedesktop platform from 24.08 to 25.08"
msgstr ""

msgid "Removed module vala as now included in freedesktop platform"
msgstr ""

msgid "Removed module libsoup as now included in freedesktop platform"
msgstr ""

msgid "Bumped libgee to 0.20.8"
msgstr ""

msgid "Sharpened some wording, fixed typos"
msgstr ""

msgid "Updated translated strings and incorporated fresh translations"
msgstr ""

msgid "i18n - Broke out Country translation to separate module"
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"i18n - Added trad Chinese, Estonian, Romaian, Tamil and Latin American "
"Spanish"
msgstr ""

msgid "New Version!"
msgstr "Nouvelle version !"

msgid "Saved Searches - new feature"
msgstr ""

msgid "Explore Genres - new feature"
msgstr ""

msgid "Jukebox Shuffle - Play Random Station - new feature"
msgstr ""

msgid "New Default Genres added"
msgstr ""

msgid "Updated look and feel"
msgstr "Amélioration ergonomie et apparence"

msgid "Station and Stream History - new feature"
msgstr ""

msgid "More Station and Stream Metadata - new feature"
msgstr ""

msgid "Save, import Starred Stations to playlists - new feature"
msgstr ""

msgid "Faster responsiveness and image loading"
msgstr ""

msgid "New data provider API, plus better support for Radio Browser"
msgstr ""

msgid "Refactored for separation of concerns, OO, maintainability"
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"Renamed, updated icons, description and screenshots per Flathub quality "
"directives"
msgstr ""

msgid "Updated HTTP Session params to improve response"
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"Increased Search re-fire interval to reduce number of concurrent searches"
msgstr ""

msgid "Made Search asynchronous so UI remains responsive during searches"
msgstr ""

msgid "Ignore request to load failing favicons URLs"
msgstr ""

msgid "Removed org.gnome.SettingsDaemon.MediaKeys from manifest per flathub"
msgstr ""

msgid "Added API server lookup via SRV and backup via JSON, plus randomization"
msgstr ""

msgid "Added JSON validation for empty nodes"
msgstr ""

msgid "Refactored libsoup calls out to HttpClient.vala"
msgstr ""

msgid "Refactored loading of favicons to Favicon.vala"
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"Turned off TLS checks for HTTP calls to avoid non loading of favicons with "
"invalid certs"
msgstr ""

msgid "Upgrade to taglib 1.13.1"
msgstr ""

msgid "Corrected README (apt libs)"
msgstr ""

msgid "Upgrade to libsoup-3.0"
msgstr ""

msgid "Fix issue where radio-browser.info API did not work"
msgstr ""

msgid "Remove Geolocation service"
msgstr ""

msgid "Change flatpak runtime to lastest eOS 6.1"
msgstr ""

msgid "Change pause button to stop button"
msgstr ""

msgid "New features:"
msgstr "Nouvelles fonctionnalités:"

msgid ""
"Background playback: Tuner can be closed and playback will continue. A "
"notification provides easy access to bring the Tuner window back."
msgstr ""

msgid "Other improvements:"
msgstr "Autres améliorations :"

msgid ""
"Dark/light mode optimized with new dropdown (use system, dark or light theme)"
msgstr ""

msgid "Dark/light mode adapts to system settings"
msgstr ""

msgid "Use elementary OS 6 flatpak runtime"
msgstr ""

msgid "Show codec and bitrate on station"
msgstr ""

msgid "New volume control"
msgstr ""

msgid "New setting: Auto-play last station"
msgstr ""

msgid "Dark mode is now saved in settings"
msgstr ""

msgid "Improved Italian translation"
msgstr ""

msgid "Properly set Window name"
msgstr ""

msgid "Added Turkish translation"
msgstr ""

msgid "Improved French translation"
msgstr ""

msgid "Minor improvements in Country name translations"
msgstr ""

msgid "Show the current track playing if supported by station"
msgstr ""
"Affichage de la piste en cours de lecture lorsque cela est pris en charge "
"par la station"

msgid "Show Top 100 stations of user country if detectable"
msgstr ""
"Affichage du top 100 des stations du pays de l'utilisateur si détectable"

msgid "\"Visit Website\" link in station context menu"
msgstr ""
"Ajout de l'option « Visiter le site Web » dans le menu contextuel des "
"stations"

msgid "Added Dutch translation"
msgstr "Ajout de la traduction en néerlandais"

msgid "Bugfixes:"
msgstr "Corrections de bug :"

msgid "Fix missing icons for non elementary OS systems"
msgstr ""
"Correction des icônes manquantes pour les systèmes différents d'elementary OS"

msgid "Add manual dark mode switch in settings"
msgstr "Ajout de l'option pour basculer au thème sombre dans les paramètres"

msgid "Compact sidebar and content window"
msgstr "Barre latérale compacte et fenêtre de contenu"

msgid "Right-click a station to add or remove to favourites directly"
msgstr ""
"Cliquez avec le bouton droit sur une station pour ajouter ou supprimer "
"directement les favoris"

msgid ""
"Add settings menu with \"Do-Not-Track\" option, disables sending station "
"listening events to radio-browser.org"
msgstr ""
"Ajout de l'option « Ne pas suivre », désactive l'envoi des événements "
"d'écoute de la station à radio-browser.org"

msgid "Add About dialog"
msgstr "Ajout de la boîte de dialogue « À propos »"

msgid ""
"If a station is already in your favourites, you'll see a little star in the "
"title"
msgstr ""
"Si une station est déjà dans vos favoris, vous verrez une petite étoile dans "
"le titre"

msgid ""
"Randomly selects one of the available radio-browser.org servers (was always "
"de1 before)"
msgstr ""
"Sélectionne au hasard l'un des serveurs radio-browser.org disponibles (était "
"toujours de1 avant)"

msgid ""
"Favourites are now stored in a local favourites.json file to improve app "
"startup time"
msgstr ""
"Les favoris sont désormais stockés dans un fichier local favourites.json "
"pour améliorer le temps de démarrage de l'application"

msgid "Added Italian translation"
msgstr "Ajout de la traduction en italien"

msgid ""
"Fix broken dark theme support (elementary and Adwaita dark look fine now)"
msgstr ""
"Correction de la prise en charge du thème sombre cassé (elementary et "
"Adwaita theme semblent bien maintenant)"

msgid "Search for radio stations"
msgstr "Recherchez des stations de radio"

msgid "New \"Genres\" section with select popular genres"
msgstr "Nouvelle section « Genres » avec une sélection de genres populaires"

msgid "Added French translation"
msgstr "Ajout de la traduction en français"

msgid "Added German translation"
msgstr "Ajout de le traduction en allemand"

msgid "Each section now displays the most-voted-for 40 stations"
msgstr "Chaque section affiche désormais les 40 stations les plus votées"

msgid "Station images are now being cached"
msgstr "Les images de station sont désormais mises en cache"

msgid "The app icon now appears more vertically centered"
msgstr "L'icône de l'application est désormais mieux centrée verticalement"

msgid "Station images are now always the same size"
msgstr "Les images de station sont désormais toujours de la même taille"

msgid "Fixed a bug where starred stations appeared as unstarred"
msgstr ""
"Correction d'un bug où les stations marquées comme favorites "
"n'apparaissaient pas comme telles"

msgid "Display a nice API error screen"
msgstr "Afficher un bel écran d'erreur d'API"

msgid "New sidebar menu with different selections and your favourite stations."
msgstr ""
"Nouveau menu dans la barre latérale avec différentes sélections et vos "
"stations favorites."

msgid "Initial release"
msgstr "Version initiale"

